				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Enrage is not a normal riposte, I get sick of people using Enrage as a reason to chime in heh.. Happens every single time no offense to anyone
<br />

<br />
For all intents and purposes, pets do not take *any* ripostes that come from the skill RIPOSTE.. Not even rarely, they dont take it
<br />

<br />
And pets riposte the same as any other PC or NPC with a maxed riposte skill, which is like 2% of the time or so
<br />

<br />
I can give you exact numbers if so inclined but dont wanna drag up logs and post them here 
<br />

<br />
